HEADWORD: Mistemper
<hw>Mis*tem"per</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To temper ill;
to disorder; <as>as, to <ex>mistemper</ex> one's head</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Warner.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
